        "content": "\"Then how comes it,\" said Monte Cristo with a frown, \"that, when I desired you to purchase for me the finest pair of horses to be found in Paris, there is another pair, fully as fine as mine, not in my stables?\" At the look of displeasure, added to the angry tone in which the count spoke, Ali turned pale and held down his head.",
